data.description: ***OFFER DEADLINE: DUE TO MULTIPLE INTEREST SELLER SET AN OFFER DEADLINE FOR FRIDAY, JANUARY 26TH. PLEASE SUBMIT YOUR OFFER BY 8PM***Welcome to this move-in ready one bedroom home located in an established, tucked-away and tranquil community of Valley Park. Conveniently located inside the Beltway it's a commuter's dream with super easy access to I395/I495/I95, within minutes from Van Dorn Metro, close to Old Town Alexandria and only 12 miles to Washington, DC.  This delightful top floor condo is a perfect gateway to comfort and convenience.  Light-filled open concept living and dining room is ideal for entertaining. Imagine walking up in your generous bedroom with floor to ceiling window, preparing a meal in your updated kitchen with Quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances and enjoying your large private balcony during Spring, Summer and Fall. This home comes with an updated bathroom and spacious closets. You will love the low condo fee, which includes water, sewer, trash, community pool, playground and grill area. Come visit and make it YOURS!
